{"title":"光辉历程","authors":["吴方"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":7,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"光辉历程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英才怀远略，雄踞井冈山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈笑挥军去，从容草檄传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旌旗空进退，壁垒早森严。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星火燎原句，烧明赤县天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二万五千里，红军作远征。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山风有剑，草地路多荆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分道回危局，全师斩巨鲸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿途播火种，举国拱辰星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南下军威壮，长江可畅游。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万船飞羽箭，一鼓定神州。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁甲沉江底，红旗上石头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麻鞋登广厦，人物自风流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国是蓝图定，航船赖指针。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多渠开富路，联产得民心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艺学先行客，门迎友谊宾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"图强应奋起，朝夕重千金。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}